{"id":230143,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":6,"day":15}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"新妇女","column":"","genre":"","count":"556","ytitle":"","mtitle":"罗美清犁田","ftitle":"","authors":["邹志坦"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"邹志坦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月桐花飞没天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷声声水满田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗美援朝大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少喜心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月分田分农具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土改后塘前大不同。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人有了好光景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新人新事说不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先说村南姓张家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个媳妇罗美清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青力壮劳动好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干出的事体人争夸!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里流传一句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“男耕女织古至今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女做家务男种地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁头不准妇人拿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢把犁头动一动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当心雷公头顶轰”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷信传说像枚针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针刺进妇女心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗美清心底细思量:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是个青年团员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产劳动要带头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能犁田怎么办?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那晚她上识字班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习不成心绪乱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底雷公多厉害，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女犁田怎不该?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了疑问大声讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上课的先生罗校长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗校长听罢不答话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把问题交给大夥儿谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一嘴来我一舌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发表意见多热烈!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说:“犁头还是不动好!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说:“迷信思想要破除。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说:“翻身农民要认清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩萨是泥塑木雕成。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的说:“穷汉没钱不烧香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛食毛着骂上苍，(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂天不但雷不打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党来把身翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地狱天堂本胡言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有神仙那有佛?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救苦救难靠自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠人民领袖毛主席!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷信害人真不浅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道理弄通她心喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来睡去眼难闭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想天光下田试一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳初露东山顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照见美清长长的影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛儿动来影儿移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的土地深深地犁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初把犁头多费力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑的脸上汗珠滴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塘前的妇女能下田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清流县人人夸奇迹!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:“毛食毛着”，清流方言，即无衣无食。(原载六月八日福建日报)"}]}